quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Sorrowful is the state of every slanderer, defamer"
  104,2,who accumulates wealth and keeps on counting it
  104,3,He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal
  104,4,"No, he will definitely be flung into the crushing one"
  104,5,And what will make you realize what the crushing one is
  104,6,"(It is the) fire of God, kindled"
  104,7,which is made to rise over the hearts
  104,8,it will certainly be closed on them
  104,9,in columns that are stretched